page_title: 'Customize a model with Azure OpenAI Service and Azure OpenAI Studio'
page_description: Learn how to create your own custom model with Azure OpenAI Service by using the Azure OpenAI Studio.
chunk_title: Review the workflow for Azure OpenAI Studio
chunk_content: Review the workflow for Azure OpenAI StudioTake a moment to review the fine-tuning workflow for using Azure OpenAI Studio:1. Prepare your training and validation data.1. Use the Create custom model wizard in Azure OpenAI Studio to train your custom model.    1. Select a base model.    1. Choose your training data.    1. Optionally, choose your validation data.    1. Optionally, configure advanced options for your fine-tuning job.    1. Review your choices and train your new custom model.1. Check the status of your custom fine-tuned model.1. Deploy your custom model for use.1. Use your custom model.1. Optionally, analyze your custom model for performance and fit.
